---
title: Beef Ragù Pasta Bar One recipe–endless ways to enjoy!
description: How do you make everyone happy at dinnertime? A DIY pasta bar! You’ll set out tender penne with two delicious sauces: a beef marinara sauce and a lemon cream sauce. Plus there’s roasted zucchini, chili flakes, and plenty of Parmesan so everyone can create their own perfect plate. Order broccoli for extra veggies, or pillowy spinach ricotta ravioli to mix it up.

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/6695610ab0a47382be870345-dc650485.jpeg
